---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<main class="content">
		<section class="panel success-panel">
			<div class="dispatch-tag">[TRANSMISSION RECEIVED]</div>
			<h1>AUDIT SIGNAL SECURED.</h1>
			<p class="lede">The transaction has been cleared. The **30-Day Structural Audit** is being dispatched to your localized terminal (email) right now.</p>
			
			<div class="hard-stop">
				<p>Check your inbox for the "Lectionary of Labor" PDF.</p>
			</div>

			<p class="note">If the signal doesn't arrive within 5 minutes, the circuit might be overloaded. Email Ezra directly and we'll manually patch the link through.</p>

			<div class="cta-row">
				<a class="btn primary" href="/">RETURN TO COMMAND CENTER (HOME)</a>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="panel">
			<h2>Next Phase: The Grounding</h2>
			<p>While you wait for the manual, you can browse the free field notes or check the maintenance log to prepare your workspace.</p>
			<div class="concept-nav">
				<a href="/maintenance-log/">View Maintenance Log</a>
				<a href="/start/">Start Here (Foundations)</a>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	.success-panel {
		border: 4px solid var(--accent);
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(178,71,45,0.1) 0%, var(--panel) 100%);
		text-align: center;
		padding: 4rem 2rem;
	}
	.success-panel h1 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
	}
	.success-panel .lede {
		margin-left: auto;
		margin-right: auto;
	}
	.success-panel .cta-row {
		margin-top: 2.5rem;
	}
</style>
